{"tid":300494,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Keto Diet 集氣區","createTime":"2017-06-28T03:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T05:22:10.000Z","uid":44338,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"815d73ed4ad03315ac6715489e7670993a64bf8c","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"食左三個禮拜，瘦左20lbs<br />\n基本上係LCHF (Low Carb High Fat)<br />\n例如，<br />\n加牛油落咖啡<br />\n盡量唔食糖，飯(少許)，同埋其他碳水化合物<br />\n<br />\n當中原理就係啟動身體對消耗脂肪嘅機制，大前提就係令身體大量減少消耗糖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲都係食緊？"},{"pid":"169762439f9df1df3bd1ee10a06ba03ae78b35db","tid":300494,"uid":75908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"食左接近3年<br />\n瘦左皮膚好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全戒粉麵飯麵包蛋糕戒糖, 係出街食麻煩啲, 偶爾會破戒<br />\n<br />\n難得呢度有同路人, KCKO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b813a91368a54632bbf6aa931edc49cd79e99460","tid":300494,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"小心酮酸中毒, 會死人㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd0762da2735847db8883d4d0b20e3942f5761b","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T08:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小心酮酸中毒, 會死人㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇到嘅資料都係輕微個案，只要腎功能冇事，可以正常産生胰島素，就唔會酮酸中毒。"},{"pid":"62be247d3d7c4b2a3bed8dcac9baa1b5cb8a9dc8","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左接近3年<br />\n瘦左皮膚好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全戒粉麵飯麵包蛋糕戒糖, 係出街食麻煩啲, 偶爾會破戒<br />\n<br />\n難得呢度有同路人, KCKO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你平時岀街食咩多？其實真係好多飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岀街冇野食"},{"pid":"51057736b902318aaa9c5c239cd4c6c9bc5e2ef2","tid":300494,"uid":8033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:46:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食左接近3年<br />\n瘦左皮膚好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全戒粉麵飯麵包蛋糕戒糖, 係出街食麻煩啲, 偶爾會破戒<br />\n<br />\n難得呢度有同路人, KCKO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你平時岀街食咩多？其實真係好多飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岀街冇野食</blockquote><br />\n好難唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b811a8611ba98acc312155cef89fd4926fa474fc","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食左接近3年<br />\n瘦左皮膚好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全戒粉麵飯麵包蛋糕戒糖, 係出街食麻煩啲, 偶爾會破戒<br />\n<br />\n難得呢度有同路人, KCKO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你平時岀街食咩多？其實真係好多飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岀街冇野食</blockquote><br />\n好難唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過真係work"},{"pid":"9e05f407d7aa3d1ccc0b6564c6d21d7963c156e4","tid":300494,"uid":73671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:42:06.000Z","msg":"有飲防彈咖啡"},{"pid":"7d3929c9838e8df5edf268eeab338de89a833f40","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有飲防彈咖啡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實同普通咖啡有冇分別？我有買佢地嘅XCT oil, so far都okay"},{"pid":"8a9a66ce1df6a7718acef51e897cd3ecdfa717f0","tid":300494,"uid":113060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T20:33:16.000Z","msg":"想試keto diet,你地有冇用啲咩app track 住啲macros?"},{"pid":"8cee7f16a878a7056292e8550e7f2583a1769abc","tid":300494,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T20:56:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0aa6a0f79a273dcdbd1fbd64b1ad7fc4dcd6b608","tid":300494,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T20:57:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c24aa4590c624c857cc266e5d56ffe1a1bce1ec","tid":300494,"uid":37414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T00:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食菜食肉 唔食碳水就ok?<br />\n炸野得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n要無炸粉"},{"pid":"b9f99337092e3b8bbee8fd999136777e371dc31a","tid":300494,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:19:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0af3c43735377383c671d49e7ac75377c1859385","tid":300494,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"967754a0fe9200e09644fc836c70fa2cd05aa568","tid":300494,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:29:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ff290abfeca1ddea27bce04265dd724448b54eb","tid":300494,"uid":52056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食菜食肉 唔食碳水就ok?<br />\n炸野得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n要無炸粉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n菜肉任食咁爽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瘋狂打邊爐<br />\n<br />\n想問身體瘦得明唔明顯<br />\n會唔會無力<br />\n可以食代糖？</blockquote><br />\n代糖/甜味劑照平時分量食幾乎冇熱量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e355364760708164a9dc8bc8059717182034a8","tid":300494,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:30:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a71a5bc2150072a2cc6a787d88d17172840d04b5","tid":300494,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:08:44.000Z","msg":"Keto有咩食物 或者簡單recipe推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都想用keto加運動減肥"},{"pid":"9e18b164176b52df80aed5252f3ff058ad06adb8","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:36:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食菜食肉 唔食碳水就ok?<br />\n炸野得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n要無炸粉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n菜肉任食咁爽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瘋狂打邊爐<br />\n<br />\n想問身體瘦得明唔明顯<br />\n會唔會無力<br />\n可以食代糖？</blockquote><br />\n開頭身體可能會因為唔適應而攰同埋頭暈。不過，捱過之後會冇事。<br />\n<br />\n體重會持續下降。<br />\n<br />\n至於糖方面，有人話甜野就唔好掂，會有類似戒癮反應，即係好似戒毒咁，好想食甜野，一食就會keep住食，一發不可收拾。<br />\n<br />\n我捱過左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dc04f3e08a4ef579172571c4018c5b0e4108fb","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Keto有咩食物 或者簡單recipe推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都想用keto加運動減肥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實開頭只要戒左碳水化合物，多菜多脂中等蛋白質。我地平時都係食開雞牛豬，只要去飯麵就可以。<br />\n<br />\n同埋，心態上唔好認為脂肪本身係差嘅營養(最好就食多啲好脂，例如三文魚，家禽，牛油果)<br />\n<br />\n我平時都會食KFC，不過因為油唔靚，所以有得揀可以少食。"},{"pid":"4f86298d55afc1b8331b0e2f20f4d6a9f5df9175","tid":300494,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小心酮酸中毒, 會死人㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同時高酮&amp;高血糖先會中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正常高酮體會令血糖降低囉"},{"pid":"d099b1049455a2d39b9f1e73d4c58761da66e1e7","tid":300494,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:45:29.000Z","msg":"記得食返啲鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b327481d14ff5ceef606235bafba7985d98f969","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想試keto diet,你地有冇用啲咩app track 住啲macros?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我其實冇用app,只係走碳水化合物，戒糖。<br />\n<br />\n另外，飯可以食，不過一日最多食一碗。因為岀街食多，所以我會有陣時食一兩啖，之後齋食肉菜，越肥越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae50c5150dc765ea7eeb478eaba17bdafaa994f","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:46:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得食返啲鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀，同埋一係列嘅vitamin B。"},{"pid":"7253ce9914c30391547b1fab89a80ee2cf6d8984","tid":300494,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:29:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>記得食返啲鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀，同埋一係列嘅vitamin B。</blockquote><br />\nB3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae73c367cfb375078f7a5b743503ca95414f9202","tid":300494,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Keto有咩食物 或者簡單recipe推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都想用keto加運動減肥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實開頭只要戒左碳水化合物，多菜多脂中等蛋白質。我地平時都係食開雞牛豬，只要去飯麵就可以。<br />\n<br />\n同埋，心態上唔好認為脂肪本身係差嘅營養(最好就食多啲好脂，例如三文魚，家禽，牛油果)<br />\n<br />\n我平時都會食KFC，不過因為油唔靚，所以有得揀可以少食。</blockquote><br />\nThx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5b10abd76140e8583eb18b42e45518e24db682","tid":300494,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Keto有咩食物 或者簡單recipe推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都想用keto加運動減肥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實開頭只要戒左碳水化合物，多菜多脂中等蛋白質。我地平時都係食開雞牛豬，只要去飯麵就可以。<br />\n<br />\n同埋，心態上唔好認為脂肪本身係差嘅營養(最好就食多啲好脂，例如三文魚，家禽，牛油果)<br />\n<br />\n我平時都會食KFC，不過因為油唔靚，所以有得揀可以少食。</blockquote><br />\nThx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n靚油係好緊要"},{"pid":"415951e42477e4c45990da8c4adfc362b7b50cc7","tid":300494,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:30:02.000Z","msg":"想問下大家嘅意見同經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我之前青春期暴肥 近大半年係低卡低carbs同高proteins低fats加運動(重訓、帶氧同pilates同拉筋都有 不過唔係日日做 同埋鳩下鳩下) 減左20kg <br />\n最快嗰期係兩個月減左六七公斤一直冇反彈 fat rate都下降左好多<br />\n不過就到左平台期 依幾個月無論做咩都係冇乜改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n一直都好想試keto 想知可唔可以boost到體脂下降 同埋大家一個月大概減到幾多？我年尾有幾個wedding同ceremonies要著晚裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想減到bmi正常<br />\n<br />\n同埋有樣野想問 我好撚重但係啲人成日以為我只係少肥 即係例如我企喺成堆BMI normal嘅朋友之間只係肥佢地少少 會唔會因為我fat rate唔算太高？ 咁樣用keto會唔會減得唔明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好想著靚靚裙去家人婚禮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過好驚<br />\n<br />\nCW: 85kg 170cm"},{"pid":"8137ffe7a2b9d59ab20e408e7717667060bc1031","tid":300494,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下大家嘅意見同經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我之前青春期暴肥 近大半年係低卡低carbs同高proteins低fats加運動(重訓、帶氧同pilates同拉筋都有 不過唔係日日做 同埋鳩下鳩下) 減左20kg <br />\n最快嗰期係兩個月減左六七公斤一直冇反彈 fat rate都下降左好多<br />\n不過就到左平台期 依幾個月無論做咩都係冇乜改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n一直都好想試keto 想知可唔可以boost到體脂下降 同埋大家一個月大概減到幾多？我年尾有幾個wedding同ceremonies要著晚裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想減到bmi正常<br />\n<br />\n同埋有樣野想問 我好撚重但係啲人成日以為我只係少肥 即係例如我企喺成堆BMI normal嘅朋友之間只係肥佢地少少 會唔會因為我fat rate唔算太高？ 咁樣用keto會唔會減得唔明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好想著靚靚裙去家人婚禮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過好驚<br />\n<br />\nCW: 85kg 170cm</blockquote><br />\n低卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKeto = 低碳水 中下蛋白 高脂<br />\n至於每樣嘅份量，個個人都唔同<br />\n太多蛋白會影響酮體嘅出現，因為多得