c=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好想著靚靚裙去家人婚禮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過好驚<br />\n<br />\nCW: 85kg 170cm</blockquote><br />\n低卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKeto = 低碳水 中下蛋白 高脂<br />\n至於每樣嘅份量，個個人都唔同<br />\n太多蛋白會影響酮體嘅出現，因為多得滯會轉為葡萄糖<br />\n<br />\n警告：本身有糖尿病，唔好亂嚟</blockquote><br />\n我指我以前係用另一套 <br />\n依家想轉keto 所以想知多啲各位同keto有關嘅經驗同效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣先可以準確啲做到keto<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點計條數</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://mariamindbodyhealth.com/keto-calculator/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmariamindbodyhealth.com%2Fketo-calculator%2F&d=AWFfUEWSyAy1hQVEKdBgyMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e192c82e\" target=\"_blank\">http://mariamindbodyhealth.com/keto-calculator/</a><br />\n自己粗粗地計下算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2b7eb3e757a7905a29824ea51a942088b45912","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:36:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下大家嘅意見同經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我之前青春期暴肥 近大半年係低卡低carbs同高proteins低fats加運動(重訓、帶氧同pilates同拉筋都有 不過唔係日日做 同埋鳩下鳩下) 減左20kg <br />\n最快嗰期係兩個月減左六七公斤一直冇反彈 fat rate都下降左好多<br />\n不過就到左平台期 依幾個月無論做咩都係冇乜改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n一直都好想試keto 想知可唔可以boost到體脂下降 同埋大家一個月大概減到幾多？我年尾有幾個wedding同ceremonies要著晚裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想減到bmi正常<br />\n<br />\n同埋有樣野想問 我好撚重但係啲人成日以為我只係少肥 即係例如我企喺成堆BMI normal嘅朋友之間只係肥佢地少少 會唔會因為我fat rate唔算太高？ 咁樣用keto會唔會減得唔明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好想著靚靚裙去家人婚禮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過好驚<br />\n<br />\nCW: 85kg 170cm</blockquote><br />\n低卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKeto = 低碳水 中下蛋白 高脂<br />\n至於每樣嘅份量，個個人都唔同<br />\n太多蛋白會影響酮體嘅出現，因為多得滯會轉為葡萄糖<br />\n<br />\n警告：本身有糖尿病，唔好亂嚟</blockquote><br />\n我指我以前係用另一套 <br />\n依家想轉keto 所以想知多啲各位同keto有關嘅經驗同效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣先可以準確啲做到keto<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點計條數</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://mariamindbodyhealth.com/keto-calculator/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmariamindbodyhealth.com%2Fketo-calculator%2F&d=AWFfUEWSyAy1hQVEKdBgyMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e192c82e\" target=\"_blank\">http://mariamindbodyhealth.com/keto-calculator/</a><br />\n自己粗粗地計下算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面嘅巴打都講得好詳盡，一語中的。<br />\n蛋白質會幫助燒脂，不過真係要睇份量，我會keep 係20-30%左右蛋白質。(有人更低，但由於生活模式局限，我都係大概維持呢個range)<br />\n<br />\n另外，keto diet嘅理論就係要令身體因為你攝取脂肪為主，而俾signal 身體--脂肪已取代碳水化合物，蛋白質，成為主糧，令到身體主然燒脂。(順手一提，會因為咁降膽固醇)<br />\n<br />\n所以，你要減肥，如果係燒脂，可以用以上原理。<br />\n<br />\n而運動本身，可以當係增加新陳代謝率，繼而令身體增加日常能量消耗(即係呼吸等日常身體運行，佔平日達70%能量消耗，而單靠運動往往只有10-20%)<br />\n<br />\n所以，正常情況下，新陳代謝能量多左，會令脂肪消耗都相應加快，係keto情況下更甚。"},{"pid":"6def9e42808660a9f30ee38b4f86c417cb3ed02b","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名學野 身體瘦得明顯？</blockquote><br />\n明顯，過脂點同埋內臟脂肪顯住下降"},{"pid":"922a52edb37e225b226acc50e1cd103849e4240e","tid":300494,"uid":120427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名學野 身體瘦得明顯？</blockquote><br />\n明顯，過脂點同埋內臟脂肪顯住下降</blockquote><br />\n我都試左三個月，好WORK<br />\n脂肪比例由22%跌到13%<br />\nMetabolic Age係17歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實際年齡32<br />\nKeto Diet前跑左半年步，減左10lbs左右(180&gt;170)冇Diet<br />\n見停左一路都冇再瘦就試Keto Diet，一個月即減多10lbs"},{"pid":"afb2fafad210a8f38a67c4d9ac57649a01da1a46","tid":300494,"uid":120427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:39:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Keto有咩食物 或者簡單recipe推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都想用keto加運動減肥</blockquote><br />\n基本上都係肉，蔬菜就係泥土以上既都食得<br />\nNuts就杏仁，夏威夷果仁 (花生，腰果就唔好喇)<br />\n水果就高纖為主例如橙，因為就算有carbs都係 indigestible carbs<br />\n飲奶就要鮮奶<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dietdoctor.com/low-carb/foods\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dietdoctor.com%2Flow-carb%2Ffoods&d=AWFfUEWSyAy1hQVEKdBgyMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ca0c6d05\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dietdoctor.com/low-carb/foods</a>"},{"pid":"965f4d72245485b400f101c83b5fb4b03064eed0","tid":300494,"uid":120427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想試keto diet,你地有冇用啲咩app track 住啲macros?</blockquote><br />\n我用MyFitnessPal，recipe好多，你甚至可以用中文SEARCH中/港式菜因為係由user upload，但亦都係因為咁所以只可作一般參考，其實都夠用<br />\n<br />\n我Keep track左一個月左右就冇keep，因為已經慢慢習慣左自己大概有個譜"},{"pid":"7660e799592563a045c571cbfd551c6c71bc1a62","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名學野 身體瘦得明顯？</blockquote><br />\n明顯，過脂點同埋內臟脂肪顯住下降</blockquote><br />\n我都試左三個月，好WORK<br />\n脂肪比例由22%跌到13%<br />\nMetabolic Age係17歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實際年齡32<br />\nKeto Diet前跑左半年步，減左10lbs左右(180&gt;170)冇Diet<br />\n見停左一路都冇再瘦就試Keto Diet，一個月即減多10lbs</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打嘅成功例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來有咁多人係食keto diet"},{"pid":"0ae1ee62fab798131de2dcb05487a58a25a40b51","tid":300494,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T00:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名學野 身體瘦得明顯？</blockquote><br />\n明顯，過脂點同埋內臟脂肪顯住下降</blockquote><br />\n我都試左三個月，好WORK<br />\n脂肪比例由22%跌到13%<br />\nMetabolic Age係17歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實際年齡32<br />\nKeto Diet前跑左半年步，減左10lbs左右(180&gt;170)冇Diet<br />\n見停左一路都冇再瘦就試Keto Diet，一個月即減多10lbs</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打嘅成功例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來有咁多人係食keto diet</blockquote><br />\n講真香港肯定好少數食keto <br />\n淨係有班on9一下就衝出嚟話會中酮毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食蛋會增加膽固醇，到依家啲醫生營養師仲係咁不停講，80%膽固醇人體自行產生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e938560c32913b405a99d18dc64ae6c5548e879","tid":300494,"uid":7409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"會唔會影響增肌"},{"pid":"157a51e402b2b7e0dbe5287a5923d7fd4b2f72f4","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名學野 身體瘦得明顯？</blockquote><br />\n明顯，過脂點同埋內臟脂肪顯住下降</blockquote><br />\n我都試左三個月，好WORK<br />\n脂肪比例由22%跌到13%<br />\nMetabolic Age係17歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實際年齡32<br />\nKeto Diet前跑左半年步，減左10lbs左右(180&gt;170)冇Diet<br />\n見停左一路都冇再瘦就試Keto Diet，一個月即減多10lbs</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打嘅成功例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來有咁多人係食keto diet</blockquote><br />\n講真香港肯定好少數食keto <br />\n淨係有班on9一下就衝出嚟話會中酮毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食蛋會增加膽固醇，到依家啲醫生營養師仲係咁不停講，80%膽固醇人體自行產生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利申，每日食四至五隻蛋，body check冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cb1a09823b4865c4963ee86e8588f0cdb0e896","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會影響增肌</blockquote><br />\n有keep住食蛋白質嫁"},{"pid":"de3f190a563921e36ab59c662757247def39cbc3","tid":300494,"uid":86377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會影響增肌</blockquote><br />\n有keep住食蛋白質嫁</blockquote><br />\n高脂飲食會唔會係短期內變肥?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6116105089d161e5a4705361eb19c9043c15398a","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會影響增肌</blockquote><br />\n有keep住食蛋白質嫁</blockquote><br />\n高脂飲食會唔會係短期內變肥?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇肥過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戒糖戒carb就可以"},{"pid":"4837d4a9ebd467454bcbe02f7c5f8083b4d89f2c","tid":300494,"uid":86377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會影響增肌</blockquote><br />\n有keep住食蛋白質嫁</blockquote><br />\n高脂飲食會唔會係短期內變肥?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇肥過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戒糖戒carb就可以</blockquote><br />\n你通常早午晚食乜? <br />\n低carb，糖都可以，但係高脂點食法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3961f387a27f5f992e6c969a43e1af5d1645b72f","tid":300494,"uid":44338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會影響增肌</blockquote><br />\n有keep住食蛋白質嫁</blockquote><br />\n高脂飲食會唔會係短期內變肥?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇肥過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戒糖戒carb就可以</blockquote><br />\n你通常早午晚食乜? <br />\n低carb，糖都可以，但係高脂點食法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/134318_f1b6b99acfe8b5c5ebfc9f4c9a6e7c3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F134318_f1b6b99acfe8b5c5ebfc9f4c9a6e7c3f.jpg&h=9bb004d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係早餐，仲有杯加左牛油椰子油咖啡。<br />\n<br />\n其實買支olive oil返黎，加返係菜到。加埋平時食雞皮，三文魚呢啲含有脂肪嘅食物。<br />\n<br />\n食脂肪好易就飽，菜本身我就會食好多，同佢佢係含有碳水化合物，所以我會戒飯麵。"},{"pid":"afcbace935e450465b1e1ecd6af439c5448cc548","tid":300494,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:52:28.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我自己都有食<br />\n<br />\n利申： 營養學家"},{"pid":"fb2b9464c33757ad8f3dd3912c86ba7442c9f85a","tid":300494,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會影響增肌</blockquote><br />\n有keep住食蛋白質嫁</blockquote><br />\n高脂飲食會唔會係短期內變肥?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇肥過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戒糖戒carb就可以</blockquote><br />\n你通常早午晚食乜? <br />\n低carb，糖都可以，但係高脂點食法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/134318_f1b6b99acfe8b5c5ebfc9f4c9a6e7c3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F134318_f1b6b99acfe8b5c5ebfc9f4c9a6e7c3f.jpg&h=9bb004d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係早餐，仲有杯加左牛油椰子油咖啡。<br />\n<br />\n其實買支olive oil返黎，加返係菜到。加埋平時食雞皮，三文魚呢啲含有脂肪嘅食物。<br />\n<br />\n食脂肪好易就飽，菜本身我就會食好多，同佢佢係含有碳水化合物，所以我會戒飯麵。</